Package org.threadly.concurrent

Class ContainerHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.threadly.concurrent.ContainerHelper
  • public class ContainerHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Class which is designed to help with determining if a Runnable or Callable is contained at some point within a chain of CallableContainer or RunnableContainer.
    Since:
    1.0.0
